SIMPLE: prompter
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prompter
<hw>Prompt"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or that which, prompts; one who admonishes
or incites to action.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who reminds another, as an actor or an orator,
of the words to be spoken next; specifically, one employed for this
purpose in a theater.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Promptitude</ent>⟦br⟧
